# Drop the documents you want recipients to access into this folder.
#
# Anything here (PDFs, images, Office files, etc.) gets pushed to the R2
# bucket by `npm run upload` and then appears on the portal automatically.
# Subfolders are preserved as part of the file's path/name.
#
# This .gitkeep file is ignored by the uploader and just keeps the empty
# folder in git.
